*Skini* svetlost i tišinu (Turn off the light and the silence).

*Skinula* je čarape i nogavice (She took off her socks and stockings).

*Skinuo* je čizme i obuću (He took off his boots and shoes).

*Skinimo* vreme i mesto (Let's forget the time and place).

*Skinuta* je udaljenost i napetost (The distance and tension were removed).

*Skinite* previše i previše (Take off too much and too much).